items.name: machine-learning-framework
items.description: A generic machine-learning framework for convenient data analysis.

items.name: ai
items.description: A collection of AI and machine learning projects covering deep learning, computer vision, NLP, and data analysis. Includes implementations of classification, clustering, PCA, and more using popular frameworks like TensorFlow, PyTorch, and Scikit-learn.

items.name: ApraPipes
items.description: A pipeline framework for developing video and image processing application. Supports multiple GPUs and Machine Learning tooklits

items.name: Hybrid-Machine-Learning-Framework-for-Water-Quality-Assessment-and-Contamination-Clustering
items.description: Hybrid Machine Learning Framework for Water Quality Assessment and Contamination Clustering in the Niger Delta

items.name: Machine-Learning
items.description: This repository explores Machine Learning (ML), covering fundamental concepts, algorithms, and hands-on projects. It includes supervised and unsupervised learning, feature engineering, model evaluation, and optimization techniques. Using frameworks like Scikit-Learn and TensorFlow, I document my learning journey and real-world applications.

items.name: os-ml-gui-lab-research
items.description: A personal research repo exploring operating system development, machine learning workflows, and cross-platform GUI applications using C/C++, Assembly, Python, and modern frameworks.

items.name: Secure-IoT-Communication-with-Mutual-Authentication-Encryption-over-MQTT
items.description: Using Hyper ledger Fabric to build a robust Blockchain Framework. Implement a sophisticated machine learning model for upgraded device authentication that does not rely on traditional crypto Analysis techniques. The resilient authentication protocol ensured the robustness of the loT system and the accuracy of the information.

items.name: ML-model-for-Pseudo-Two-Dimensional-P2D-lithium-ion-battery-prediction
items.description: machine learning and electrochemical modeling to perform parameter identification for a Pseudo Two-Dimensional (P2D) lithium-ion battery model. The goal is to develop a robust machine learning framework that can accurately identify and optimize the parameters of the P2D model using experimental data.

items.name: ihp-framework
items.description: Integrative Historical Prediction (IHP) Framework: Analyzing and forecasting complex societal phenomena. Combines Riemannian geometry, network theory, and machine learning to model societal dynamics. Includes case studies on Arab Spring, cryptocurrency adoption, and climate migration. Advanced math meets data science meets history meets AI fiction.

items.name: pyroml
items.description: Machine Learning framework allowing plug-and-play training for pytorch models

items.name: AiML-credit-risk---loan-optimization-ml
items.description: This project focuses on leveraging advanced data analytics and machine learning techniques to develop a comprehensive credit risk assessment, credit scoring, and loan optimization framework.

items.name: OpenAI-ML-SDK
items.description: OpenAI-ML-SDK is a generic Machine Learning SDK and API framework inspired by real-world industrial AI projects. It allows users to run distributed machine learning workflows (like K-Means clustering) through a Python SDK connected to a FastAPI backend powered by Apache Spark and frontend with Bokeh for a rich, interactive user experience.

items.name: scclv2
items.description: SCalable Continual Learning - An experimental machine learning framework for the investigation of continual learning algorithms.
